Description: Provides IDESCAT sea temperature data of Costa Brava, 2000-2017,
    and tools to analyze temperature changes and anomalies. 
    Includes functions to calculate month-to-month changes, 
    compute anomalies relative to 1974-1999 baseline, create visualizations,
    and perform trend analysis. Data and baseline are included in the package.
